channel.title: What game should I do a Let's Play of next?
channel.description:
Hey guys, I'm making this quick little poll. Seeing as how my video on YouTube rendered useless, I thought I'd ask here. So the question is simple: What game should I do a Let's Play of next? I asked this on YouTube, but i only got two votes, so yeah. Please help :smiley:
EDIT: By the way, those two votes are for XIII and L4D. And this poll will be closed two weeks from now... so yeah
